This is the first of two monographs—long articles or short books on a particular subject—published to support Jim Collins' business classic <strong><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1709484164" target="_blank">Good to Great</a>.</strong> The other was <strong><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2918727125" target="_blank">Turning the Flywheel</a>.</strong>



Access Gene Babon's reviews of books on <strong>Business Leadership</strong> and <strong>Business Strategy</strong> at <strong><a href="https://www.pinterest.com/webapprentices/" target="_blank">Pinterest</a>.</strong>
